subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Vera Zvonareva defeated Kaia Kanepi, 6-3, 7-5, while top-seeded Caroline Wozniacki beat Dominika Cibulkova by 6-2, 7-5 on the same court — but in a worse wind.
